ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCanada - Kingdom of Denmark ** Agreement **
PrecisOrder authorizing (1) the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT BETWEEN THE GOVERNMENT OF CANADA ON THE ONE HAND AND THE GOVERNMENT OF THE KINGDOM OF DENMARK TOGETHER WITH THE GOVERNMENT OF GREENLAND ON THE OTHER HAND ON THE MARITIME AND LAND BOUNDARIES IN THE AREA BETWEEN CANADA AND GREENLAND; or (2) the Minister of Foreign Affairs to execute and issue an Instrument of Full Powers, authorizing the individuals mentioned in the order to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the Agreement.
AttachmentsAttachment
